  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div>\n\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Prerequisites: Strength 13 or higher</i></p>\n\t\t\t<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You've developed the skills necessary to hold your own in close-quarters grappling. You gain the following benefits:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on attack rolls against a creature you are grappling.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You can use your action to try to pin a creature <a href=\"https://5e.tools/conditionsdiseases.html#grappled_phb\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'conditionsdiseases.html', 'PHB', 'grappled_phb', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >grappled</a> by you. To do so, make another grapple check. If you succeed, you and the creature are both <a href=\"https://5e.tools/conditionsdiseases.html#restrained_phb\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'conditionsdiseases.html', 'PHB', 'restrained_phb', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >restrained</a> until the grapple ends.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t</div>",
